# Heirlift Estate Services — Live Executive Dashboard

## Setup on Render.com (recommended — free tier)

1. Push this repo to GitHub
2. Go to render.com → New Web Service → connect your repo
3. Set environment variables:
   - SF_USERNAME = kyle@simplysellnw.com
   - SF_PASSWORD = your Salesforce password
   - SF_TOKEN = your Salesforce security token
4. Deploy — get a permanent URL like https://heirlift-dashboard.onrender.com

## Local development
```
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# fill in .env with your SF credentials
node server.js
```
